Package: Euclimatch
Type: Package
Title: Euclidean Climatch Algorithm
Version: 0.1.1
Author: Justin A.G. Hubbard, D. Andrew R. Drake, Nicholas E. Mandrak
Maintainer: Justin A.G. Hubbard <justin.hubbard@mail.utoronto.ca>
Description: Interface for performing climate matching using the Euclidean "Climatch" algorithm. Functions provide the percent of climatch scores >=6, mean climatch score, and a vector of climatch scores within the recipient region. Tools for parallelization and visualizations also provided.
License: GPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
Imports: Rcpp (>= 1.0.10), foreach, doParallel, RcppParallel, terra, RColorBrewer, grDevices
LinkingTo: Rcpp
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
